gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要有火燒，破壞店鋪已經構成暴動！正苦就係希望呢三日一拉告暴動，前線點做，有你哋主意，但怕被推入陷阱。<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔，唔好見怪"},{"pid":"970baac849f3a9fc58406b4b6bb6db7e34ebfeda","tid":1627094,"uid":209106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be5cfff102b3f9bee57d7cbc0d1e26faf6da0a8","tid":1627094,"uid":209106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5ce18b70d25296cfbc672c92e8f5c158133206","tid":1627094,"uid":209106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}